#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/smallrye-fault-tolerance.adoc:429
msgid "To test this out, do the following:"
msgstr "これを試すには、次のようにします。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/smallrye-fault-tolerance.adoc:431
